data.description: Welcome home! This townhome offers a well designed open floor plan, 9ft ceilings and archways, providing the ideal setting for creating lasting memories with family and friends. The main living area features a welcoming living room and  dining area that flows into the contemporary kitchen and sun-drenched south facing private patio, offering an  indoor/outdoor living experience. The primary bedroom is generously proportioned and showcases an expansive walk-in closet, providing ample storage for your personal belongings. Pamper yourself in the en-suite bath designed to provide a soothing and relaxing ambiance. Additionally, there are two spacious bedrooms that can comfortably accommodate a queen-sized bed or a home office, offering versatile living options, along with a full-sized bathroom and dedicated laundry room with washer/dryer and built-in cabinetry. Convenience is further enhanced with a one-car attached garage, ensuring that all your storage needs are met effortlessly.Low maintenance landscaping.The HOA $198/monthly dues include exterior building maintenance and roof. Close to schools, restaurants, shopping and parks. Minutes to 101.
